  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. The model predicts absolute hemolysis index for a Class III VAD device operating at Model Risk Level 5 across the clinical flow envelope (3–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM). Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed across all 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors. Seven factors are formally assessed; six are flagged as epistemic gaps. All assessed factors achieve their required gradation levels under the Minimal profile review scope. Decision: Accepted under Minimal profile with acknowledged epistemic gaps documented in the decision record.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-cfd-requirement",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/cfd-hemolysis-vad-absolute-prediction",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/fda-centrifugal-pump-cfd-hemolysis-v3",
